values:
Hello everyone.  this journal is going to be a rant mostly...but i may make it persinal sometimes...so here it goes.

Dear Xero,
Im one of those kids that was never expected to be more than a social outcast, not even my close friends respect me for anything but my elet gaming skills.  But recintly I find myself being happy.  I was so lucky to get the girlfriend i have, and kind of supprised.  Shes sexey and beautifal and no matter how i feel or whats wrong she makes me feel better.  But since im not the most popular kid in school(like the lower 5%) she has been getting crap from people at school.  Im used to getting crap but it is affecting her.  I just want her to be happy again.  So untill she is ill be here for her.

some people are just compleetly stupid.  i wish i could do somthing to make them stop, but im not going to give them the satisfaction.  And now the stress has her sick.  I just hope that everything gets better soon.

"Untill the end of time i shall be in this pergatory that i have made and i will fight my way back to you...and if anyone tries to stop me i will take heaven and hell down with me." -DeathScyth Arcana
